User Story 2: Login/Authentication

Upon reaching the home page of the website, the user will be presented with basic login functionality.The user will be presented with a login button. After passing oauth the site will inform the new visitor about signing up if they are not already.  
Upon submitting their online profile, the user will be redirected to a event page where they are prompted to enter their interest. If the credentials are incorrect, the user will be redirected back to the same page and an error message will be displayed to 
indicate incorrect credentials. If the login is successful, the user will be redirected to the user home page, which will present basic information
about events depending on whether they have much money to spend or not and provide them options such as planning a new night out or viewing the weather. 
